data.description: Gorgeous end unit townhome in desirable Walnut Creek neighborhood! The open floorplan showcases a fully upgraded kitchen with granite countertops, an oversized kitchen island, stainless steel appliances, and stylish finishes. A convenient computer nook is located off the kitchen and perfect for remote work or studying. Designated drop zone area downstairs to keep everything organized. Upstairs, there's a spacious loft and laundry room with plenty of storage space. Each bathroom boasts upgraded finishes and granite countertops. Beyond your doorstep, Walnut Creek offers amazing community amenities like the pool, playground, clubhouse, tennis courts, and more! Conveniently located near Indian Land, Waxhaw, and Ballantyne, with ample shopping and dining options and top-rated Indian Land schools. Come and experience the perfect blend of comfort and convenience!
